## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all possible strategies or the latest research developments in bullying prevention. Additionally, the effectiveness of these strategies can vary based on the specific context and implementation within individual schools. Further research and localized studies may be necessary to tailor these recommendations to specific school environments.